# Production environment
# NOTE: Vite does NOT support indirection like `.env.local.VAR_NAME`.
# Values in env files must be literal values.
#
# In production, provide these at build-time (or create an uncommitted `frontend/.env.local` for local dev):
# - VITE_NEO4J_URI=neo4j+s://<id>.databases.neo4j.io
# - VITE_NEO4J_USER=<username>
# - VITE_NEO4J_PASSWORD=<password>
# - VITE_NEO4J_DATABASE=<optional database name>
#
# Optional Ollama settings for features that call Ollama directly from the browser:
# - VITE_OLLAMA_API_URL=http://localhost:11434
# - VITE_OLLAMA_MODEL=deepseek-r1:7b